{"tid":1755013,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"又有嘉年華feel啦","createTime":"2019-11-25T11:59:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-26T14:40:20.000Z","uid":17360,"like":19,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d366accdec4ae10154b47a181cc8bff0a0226d0d","tid":1755013,"uid":17360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T11:59:50.000Z","msg":"求下你地唔好咁啦<br />\n<br />\n點對得住犧牲咗既人啊？<br />\n<br />\n係咪要再有人死先知衰？<br />\n<br />\n踢一腳先郁一下<br />\n<br />\n咁樣革乜撚野命 區選只係件小事<br />\n<br />\n大事未成 你地就覺得夠？"},{"pid":"a9d8f49fc87802c678576eec960fe4495a73c36a","tid":1755013,"uid":17360,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T12:01:17.000Z","msg":"btw 而家係尖東手足同理大手足<br />\n<br />\n加油，唔好放棄"},{"pid":"9f46eccffffd22413893aa0525081d00d56e4416","tid":1755013,"uid":23672,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T12:02:50.000Z","msg":"尖東手足 等理大手足傾好先 唔洗激動住"},{"pid":"326cce82b97bb4df5bc3528842f238e4deadc36a","tid":1755013,"uid":1241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9f46eccffffd22413893aa0525081d00d56e4416","tid":1755013,"uid":23672,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T12:02:50.000Z","msg":"尖東手足 等理大手足傾好先 唔洗激動住"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T12:04:20.000Z","msg":"等到發叔都翻生啦等撚夠未<br />\n傾撚到幾時？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/dog_hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4717fdf0bc1618183f413e4aa4ae70edcde7910","tid":1755013,"uid":38109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T12:06:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76e24e27da899830318e9a86eb13435aba4b8092","tid":1755013,"uid":17360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T12:13:37.000Z","msg":"而家呢個moment 更加要養精蓄銳<br />\n<br />\n物資，文宣，裝備<br />\n<br />\n呢三樣野都短缺<br />\n<br />\n醒目就趁風聲不大<br />\n<br />\n儘量儲備好，以備不時之需<br />\n<br />\n因為班狗已經返唔到轉頭<br />\n<br />\n佢地唔會就此罷手<br />\n<br />\n敵進我守，敵退則攻<br />\n<br />\n唔好比佢地抖夠再精氣神滿電<br />\n<br />\n狠狠地打手足甚至無辜既人<br />\n<br />\n我希望下次見到 係主動出擊<br />\n<br />\n而唔係成班垃圾防暴出曬黎<br />\n<br />\n先知要開始打<br />\n<br />\n同埋要更加有組織，一波上<br />\n<br />\n一波退，一波又一波，源源不斷<br />\n<br />\n撤退方法同路線要諗好<br />\n<br />\n最好有幾條路線撤 仲要一齊用<br />\n<br />\n唔好行曬一條路線撤"},{"pid":"4e1eb6a67e10702766d2e986cb8cfb7bfab4a365","tid":1755013,"uid":23989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T12:18:36.000Z","msg":"已經唔開心左好多日<br />\n係最近先有好消息<br />\n比我開心埋今晚啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6814a5e1344e2b4becd7ae767d6c3a44a5ca56f1","tid":1755013,"uid":17360,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4e1eb6a67e10702766d2e986cb8cfb7bfab4a365","tid":1755013,"uid":23989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T12:18:36.000Z","msg":"已經唔開心左好多日<br />\n係最近先有好消息<br />\n比我開心埋今晚啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T12:22:47.000Z","msg":"開心埋今日好啦<br />\n<br />\n唔好唔記得 呢個好消息背後<br />\n<br />\n有幾多人死得不明不白<br />\n<br />\n有幾多手足慘遭凌辱<br />\n<br />\n如果開心得落 都幾有病"},{"pid":"59cd62ea7d0171a4eac091f7dee7eee71fdfdcc6","tid":1755013,"uid":17360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T12:25:18.000Z","msg":"拉"},{"pid":"ff41db516cecdd65835fb4ddcbafd28b59f0213c","tid":1755013,"uid":17360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T12:27:01.000Z","msg":"拉"},{"pid":"fd05a346cc419b37315f4beb964f3f7f924c33dc","tid":1755013,"uid":17360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedB